  "instructions": [
    "In a bowl, combine the crumbled tofu, minced black olives, diced ginger, minced garlic, sliced scallions, soy sauce, rice wine, sesame oil, cornstarch, salt, and pepper until well mixed.",
    "Place a teaspoon of the filling onto each dumpling wrapper.",
    "Fold each wrapper in half and pinch the edges together, adding a little water to seal.",
    "Line a steamer basket with parchment paper and arrange the dumplings without touching.",
    "Bring water to a boil and steam the dumplings over high heat for 8 minutes.",
    "Remove the dumplings from the steamer and let them rest for one minute.",
    "Serve hot with a small bowl of light soy dipping sauce."
  ],
